OL,3,CAntarctica: UK charity seeks recruits
OL,4,Cin world's southernmost Post Office
OL,6,FDoes conducting penguin counts sound
OL,7,Fup your street or perhaps sorting mail
OL,8,Fat a not so ordinary workplace?
OL,10,FIf so, you could be just the right fit
OL,11,Fto work at what has been dubbed the
OL,12,Fworld's southernmost Post Office.
OL,14,FThe UK Antarctic Heritage Trust
OL,15,F(UKAHT) is now accepting applications
OL,16,Ffor its 2024-25 season, and is seeking
OL,17,Fintrepid adventurers to take on a
OL,18,Frange of roles at its base in Port
OL,19,FLockroy, Antarctica - located around
OL,20,F9,000 miles from the UK
