OL,3,CAntarctica: UK charity seeks recruits
OL,4,Cin world's southernmost Post Office
OL,6,F"From sorting mail at the world's
OL,7,Fsouthernmost post office to posting
OL,8,Fpenguin memes, UKAHT has job
OL,9,Fopportunities you won't find anywhere
OL,10,Felse," the UKAHT says on its .
OL,12,FApplicants are wanted to spend five
OL,13,Fmonths living and working in the
OL,14,Fremote British territory, and can
OL,15,Fapply to take on one of five roles,
OL,16,Fwhich include base leader, shop
OL,17,Fmanager and general assistant.
