OL,3,CAntarctica: UK charity seeks recruits
OL,4,Cin world's southernmost Post Office
OL,6,FThe UKAHT said it is particularly
OL,7,Finterested to hear from anyone who has
OL,8,Fexperience and skills in customer
OL,9,Fservice, wildlife monitoring and
OL,10,Fgeneral maintenance, amongst other
OL,11,Fareas.
OL,13,FIf accepted, you could be responsible
OL,14,Ffor helping to welcome up to 18,000
OL,15,Fvisitors to the island, perform
OL,16,Fmaintenance and upkeep tasks of
OL,17,Fhistoric buildings and artefacts or
OL,18,Frun Port Lockroy's charity gift shop.
