OL,3,CAntarctica: UK charity seeks recruits
OL,4,Cin world's southernmost Post Office
OL,6,FPort Lockroy has no access to Wi-Fi or
OL,7,Frunning water, so potential applicants
OL,8,Fshould be aware they will need to be
OL,9,Fresilient, physically fit and
OL,10,Fenvironmentally aware.
OL,12,FAnyone interested has until Monday
OL,13,FMarch 18 to apply, with training due
OL,14,Fto start in August.
OL,16,FSuccessful candidates will then
OL,17,Fcommence their stints in the Antarctic
OL,18,Fbetween late 2024 to March the
OL,19,Ffollowing year.
